y every moment of your stay at the end of days.<br><br><i>**Use at own risk. Slaycation Paradise Ltd. Accepts no liability for injury or zombie plague infections sustained.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Take advantage of our premium weapons and turret rental catalogue</h2><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643850/extras/4-Weapons.gif?t=1689322961\" /><br><br>Enjoy our apocalypse-proof weapon selection from the classic pump shotgun to the flamethrower, cat-launcher, magic wands and many, many more. Whether it\u2019s cutting through mobs like butter or battling Kaiju-sized monsters, our incredible arsenal brings laughter to the slaughter.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Earn Slaycation Club Member\u2019s Rewards</h2><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643850/extras/5-Perks.gif?t=1689322961\" /><br><br>We like to give back to our members here at Slaycation Paradise. While touring with us, you'll earn Slaycation Club Rewards, allowing you to unlock new apocalyptic destinations, crazy new weapons or wonderful upgrade perks. Only the best will do for our valued customers!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Cleared Orientation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1643850/4cec40c0a7f26cd42b055c8a708b4152c2f44533.jpg"},{"name":"Premium Economy upgrade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1643850/217d3a15903ef6ab112755f8a43f65273aa39e84.jpg"},{"name":"Business Class upgrade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1643850/37faedb11e88fbea6dc5c67d7325fbaa0c1b54b4.jpg"},{"name":"First Class upgrade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1643850/c993fdbc4338c1584e3bf22eabdba7518a738268.jpg"},{"name":"Living life on easy mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps